consensus text: 100 grains of Barilla gave (by dissolving them in
50 grains of carbonate of Ammonia & by filtering
the solution & exposing the residuum for some time
to a red heat. 57 grains of quick Lime - The liquid
which passed through the filter when evaporated
to dryness left 2 3/4 grains of saline matter.
100 grains of [unclear]Kelp[/unclear] treated in the same manner &
with the same quantity of Carbonate of ammonia
gave 59 grains of quick-lime & 1 1/4 grain of
3 of the Gas & 2 of Oxyg[superscript]e[/superscript]. diminish'd to 2
one measure of Nit[superscript]r[/superscript] gas added dimin to 1 1/2
